review:
I give 1 star because I cannot give 0 when submitting the review:
1. Not able to contact them when order never comes;
2. Cannot see the order status sometimes, you cannot do anything but keep waiting until you gave up;
3. Use grabfood and Deliveroo bah,they are much better even if the delivery fee is higher but at least you can get your food.
